description: Mixed use redevelopment comprising fifty six 1-bedroomed, eight 1/2-bedroomed and forty six 2-bedroomed flats together with 1200 sq metres of B1 office floor space in one 9-storey and one 12-storey building together with basement car and cycle parking, plant, refuse and amenity facilities and alterations to access (amendment to previously approved app No. B2004/52951/FUL comprising substitution of six 3-bedroomed flats with twelve 2-bedroomed flats).
